      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 66-71.</p><p>Greater Metamagic</p><p>Also at 20th level, you learn 2 greater metamagic options. These work in the same way as regular metamagic options, but they expend Legendary Points instead of Sorcery Points. You learn another greater metamagic option when you reach 22nd and 24th levels.</p></div>",
